description: Barcode Professional SDK for .NET is a lightweight .NET assembly (DLL) which can be used for adding advanced barcode capabilities such as barcode image generation and printing to any .NET Framework-based applications. Features: - Linear, Postal, MICR & 2D Barcode Symbologies - Crystal Reports for .NET / ReportViewer RDLC support - Save barcode images in image files as well as in stream objects - GIF, BMP, PNG, JPEG-JPG, EMF, EPS & TIFF barcode image formats support - Visual Studio, Visual Basic, Visual C# - .NET Data Binding support, High Quality Printing support (PrintDocument) - Supported Barcodes - Australia Post 4-state Barcode, ABC Codabar, USS Code 128 A-B-C, USS Code 39, USS Code 93, Data Matrix ECC200, Deutsche Post Identcode, Deutsche Post Leitcode, EAN-13, GTIN-13, EAN-8, GTIN-8, EAN-99, Coupon Barcode, EAN-Velocity, Industrial 2 of 5, Standard 2 of 5, Interleaved 2 of 5, ITF 25, ISBN, Bookland EAN, ISBN-13, ISBN-10, ISMN, ISSN, ITF-14, EAN-14, DUN-14, GTIN-14, JAN-13, JAN-8, MSI, OPC, PDF417, Portable Data File 417, PDF417 Truncated, PLANET, POSTNET, PZN, British Royal Mail 4-State Customer Barcode, RM4SCC, Royal TPG Post KIX 4-State Barcode, SCC-14, Singapore 4-State Postal Code Barcode, SSCC-18, UPC-128, EAN-18, Swiss PostParcel Barcode, UCC-EAN-128, EAN-128, GTIN-128, UPC-A, UPC-E, GTIN-12, USPS Sack Label, USPS Tray Label Barcode, QR Code, USPS FIM, USPS Horizontal Bars, Telepen, Pharmacode, Semacode, Code 32 Italian Pharmacode IMH, USPS Package Identification Code (PIC), FedEx Ground 96, HIBC LIC/PAS, ISBT 128, Italian Post 25, USPS Intelligent Mail Barcode, Aztec Code, Compact PDF417, Macro PDF417, Micro PDF417, Micro QR Code, UPS MaxiCode, GS1 DataBar, RSS-14, GS1 DataMatrix, MICR E-13-B, ALL EAN.UCC Composite Barcodes CC-A, CC-B, CC-C, USPS Intelligent Mail Container Barcode, Han Xin Code, Japan Post 4state, Korea Post, Datalogic, Swiss-QRCode, JAB-Code Multicolored, 2D-Pharmacode, Plessey, TriOptic, EPC QR Code, Code49, Codablock F, TLC39

summary: The most reliable barcode component for .NET apps. It supports Linear (1D), Postal, MICR, Composite and 2D Symbologies. Visual Studio, ReportViewer RDLC and Crystal Reports .NET support.
title: Barcode Pro SDK for .NET
